    "content": "<p>Prepare to be amazed as Maximus Payus showers you with bonuses and features that will make your head spin! Not even Julius Caesar could resist the temptation of 8 free spins that come with three Bonus symbols. Aim higher and hit 4 Bonus symbols, and you're in for 15 free spins. But if you want to reign supreme, five special symbols will reward you with 20 free spins. And guess what? You can even re-trigger Bonus symbols during free spins, with additional 5, 8, 15 or 20 spins!</p><p>But that's not all: brace yourself for two entirely random bonuses that could rain riches on your reels. One will give you a level win or even pay 20x; the other will generously award 5 or more identical symbols. Get ready to multiply your gains as Maximus Payus takes you on a wild ride you won't forget!</p>"
}

